Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/Perolehan/001 Left Menu Selection/Select Menu Pesanan Tempatan
Description: Select Perolehan and then select Pesanan Tempatan
Open browser and input homepage URL
Click on Menu Sisi to display Menu selections

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/Perolehan/002 Rekod Baru oleh Penyedia/001 Penyedia Rekod Baru

Description: Click on Rekod Baru to create new record

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/Perolehan/002 Rekod Baru oleh Penyedia/002 Senarai Semak
Test Cases/Perolehan/002 Rekod Baru oleh Penyedia/003 Sah Simpan

Description: Select Pesanan Tempatan - Jumlah untuk disahkan from Dashboard
Select first row from the list of Senarai Tugas
Get todays date with format dd/MM/yyyy
verify tahun kewangan matches current year
verify tarikh semasa matches system date
verify that jumlah pesanan tempatan is same as the record created by penyedia
Click on Sah button to sah
click on Ya to confirm sah
click on OK to close the prompt after Sah is complete
Select Pesanan Tempatan - Jumlah untuk diluluskan
Double click on item no 1 from senarai tugas
Get todays date with format dd/MM/yyyy
verify tahun kewangan matches current year
verify tarikh semasa matches system date
take only the record ID which is from index 29 until 44
set global variable value of RekodID with variable RekodNo
verify jumlah is matched with the one created by Penyedia which is 6.25
Click on Lulus button to approve
click on Ya to confirm approve
click on OK to close the prompt after lulus is complete

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/Perolehan/005 Terimaan Barang Perkhidmatan/001 Proses Kemasukan Terimaan Barang

Description: Open browser and navigate to Homepage URL
Click on Menu Sisi to display Menu selections
Click on Drop down Jenis Pertanyaan
Click on value Pesanan Tempatan auto
Set text no rekod that is generated from test case Pelulus
Click on button Cari to find the record
Click OK to close the prompt box
Get no dokumen from the record
Click on Menu Sisi to display Menu selections
Click on Menu sisi Kemasukan Terimaan Barang atau perkhidmatan
Set text RekodID based on the variable get from Pelulus page on Pesanan Tempatan
Click on OK to close the prompt box
Click on drop down Jenis terimaan
Click on Date Picker to select tarikh terimaan
Double click on the field to make it editable
Input value for Dihantar using spinner - click until 5 times
Input value for Diterima using spinner - click until 5 times
Click Simpan to save the record
Click OK to close the prompt box
Click Ya to confirm Sah Simpan
Take screenshot of the rekod ID
Click OK to close the prompt box
